items: Ludouico Sforza. a supposed Duke of Millaine.
Tiberio. two Lords of his Counsell. Stephano.
Pescara, a Marquesse, and friend to Sforza.
Graccho. a creature of Mariana sister to Sfozra.
Hernando Captaines to the Emperour. Medina
Marcelia. the Dutches wife to Sforza.
Mariana. wife to Francisco, and sister to Sforza.
